description: free +‎ booty +‎ -er. Calque of Dutch vrijbuiter (literally “free booty-er”), from vrij (“free”) + buit (“booty”) + -er (occupational suffix). Doublet of filibuster.

entries.meaning: An adventurer who pillages, plunders or wages ad-hoc war on other nations.
One who rehosts online media without authorization; one who freeboots.
